            <title>[DERBY-4885] Reduce lock timeout in SavepointJdbc30Test</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-4885</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There&apos;s a test case in SavepointJdbc30Test that waits a minute for a lock timeout to happen. The test case runs in four different configurations, so it spends four minutes just waiting. We should lower the lock timeout to make the test run faster.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
